original_title: Skálmöld 10 Year Anniversary Live In Reykjavik
overview: Viking Metal ice giants SKÁLMÖLD will release their new live album, 10 Year Anniversary - Live In Reykjavík, on September 25, 2020. The album was recorded during their three consecutive sold-out shows at the Gamla Bíó, Reykjavík, Iceland and transports the mythical atmosphere directly into the listener's home.
title: Skálmöld 10 Year Anniversary Live In Reykjavik
